casebody.data:
Thursday, January 5, 1995

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-1415. No. 65217. Carlin v. Mambuca. Cuyahoga County,

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal and cross-appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the joint application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective January 4, 1995.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
